            <lg xml:id="TK56">
<l>taṟkāttut taṟkoṇṭāṟ pēṇit takaicāṉṟa</l>
<l>coṟkāttuc cōrvilāḷ peṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She who guards herself, cherishes the one who took her, guards words</l>
<l>abounding in propriety, unwearying—that is a woman.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
